phrases: To be honest, I thought girls would be a lot more work.
You are not possessive, and you do not get selfish.
I guess there are girls like you.
I want to be possessive, and I want to be selfish.
I get a bit jealous when I see him talk to other girls.
I want to be connected with him from good morning to good night.
I want to cling onto him and cuddle right now.
But if I told him that, he might think I am a pain.
D-Do not you ever feel possessive about me, Goda-kun?
I hear those kinds of relationships do not last.
But do not you think it is okay in moderation?
I guess a little is fine.
For example, holding our hands when we walk.
We do not have to, if you do not want to.
You do not need to be that cautious.
Th-Then can I come closer to you?
Y-Yeah, if that is what you want.
Is it okay if I am this close?
I do not mind, but I might smell from club
What is gotten into you today?
Do you not like clingy people?
But you said that is a pain.
Is not this normal if we are dating?
I actually thought you did not like being clingy.
I thought you did not think about it.
Do you want to cuddle more, then?
I would not have held back if you would told me.
All right, can I make a request, too, then?
I have always wanted to do that once.
I choked on my first kiss!
I choked on my first kiss!
I was not prepared at all.
I coughed on my first kiss...
I coughed on my first kiss...
I coughed on my first kiss...
I coughed on my first kiss...
Rumor had it that a guy in my class kissed his girlfriend.
They have only been together for three months.
Man, they did not look like they would take it so fast.
I wanted to talk to you about that.
They have had so many opportunities already.
Why do you think they cannot score, Coach?
The forward, Chiaki, keeps chickening out.
But Coach, his teammates have to pass him the ball.
It is not just Chiaki's fault
Should I pass to you now, then?
Kamine and Goda scored a shot in the park, I hear.
Everyone seems to think we have at least kissed already.
Well, does it matter how long we have been dating,
or if other people have already kissed?
What matters most is improving our own game.
Well, you want to, do not you?
Not if you feel like you are being forced.
Shit, this is where she refuses to talk to you for a while.
She is totally waiting for me!
I cannot get near the goal, though the audience has their eyes fixed.
I am going to have to just go for it.
But I kissed a girl on the face for the first time.
Coach, I would like to go again.
I feel like I can do it now.
I think I am getting pretty good at English.
Maybe it is thanks to you.
Let me squeeze your boobs, then.
Akagi, dude, we are in the Library.
Are not we here to study for exams because we mess around too much at home?
Let me squeeze your boobs, Ryoko-chan.
You say some of the dumbest shit for someone that is as smart as you.
Why would I let you touch my boobs when there are so many people around?
I am sure you will let me squeeze them if I ask persistently enough.
But am I the only one holding back?
Do not you feel like messing around more?
I am telling you to come here.
I told you, I am not really...
You do not have to hold back.
But in return, let me squeeze your boobs a little.
Are you telling me to hold back while you run free?
It is your fault for tempting me.
So I can squeeze your boobs, then?
All right, let us get back to studying.
I never intended to feel you up.
Even though you were ready to let me.
Then why did you say all that?
I wanted you to know how much I am holding back all the time.
You say that like I am the only one being needy!
I feel better, now that you understand.
My love was like a sparkler.
The fragile spark of passion has burnt out.
But the image of its vibrant light still shines in my mind.
This is where I first met him.
I am sorry, I do not remember every girl's face.
I might remember if I see your smile.
Ah, the little kitten from before.
I made a taken girl fall for me again.
Say, little kitten, how can I become less popular?
I cannot tell him it is impossible.
But you are so beat up!
They are probably waiting for me at home.
I will have to be a stray cat for a while.
Th-Then, why do not you come to my place?
Stay near me, and you will die.
You do not get it, little kitten.
The people chasing me are not my true enemy.
There is only one man who could make me that way.
As long as the god of dating implores me to be popular, I will hurt someone again.
I do not want to hurt anyone anymore.
You are the one who is hurt!
I am impressed you can keep up with me.
You are not ready for these moves.
Still, I want to be with you!
Or perhaps you are a fine leopardess now.
Watch me stop you with one finger.
Who do you think I am?
Do you honestly think you can stop me with one finger?
Fall for me even more, and you will suffer more than just burns.
Am I not good enough for you?
If you are prepared for that, then burn.
I would make a bad senpai if I let my juniors play with fire.
I am going to go beat the crap out of the god of romance
so that I do not get any more popular.
Until then, be careful around fires of love.
